Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:18.35,Haiyore-internal/narrator,creepy 2,0000,0000,0000,,{I knew it was weird, being \Nreleased all of a sudden.}Hm, mình biết mà, tự nhiên mấy ổng đưa mình xuống đây làm việc.
